Title: Making a technical change to a provision requiring a petition in a summary proceeding to recover possession of real property in the city of Syracuse to allege proof of compliance with local laws
Summary: Makes a technical change to a provision requiring a petition in a summary proceeding to recover possession of real property in the city of Syracuse to allege proof of compliance with local laws requiring the registration or licensure of residential rental dwellings.
LawSection: Real Property Actions and Proceedings Law
LawCode: Amd ยง741, RPAP L (as proposed in S.3497 & A.3110)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the real property actions and proceedings law, in relation to making a technical change to a provision requiring a petition in a summary proceeding to recover possession of real property in the city of Syracuse to allege proof of compliance with local laws
